{"_type":"event","item_id":"019eb35d52957a339ef7b7e6a64f3107","seq":5,"event_type":"transition","actor":"agent","timestamp":"2026-06-10T21:37:57","note":"in_progress → done. Shipped plugins main dae77ea. Gate semantics: settle_prompt turn_completed counts only after busy (spinner) or row growth past arm/start reference; gate closes on arm/watch_start/counted turn; bell/dialog/exit bypass. Live-verified: fresh watch on idle screen shows NO phantom (status stays null through multiple wait cycles); armed send fires exactly once after the real turn. 2 integration regressions + is_busy unit test. Bonus: all_turns no longer re-fires on the same idle screen."}
